org.openimaj.image.model.asm.datasets

Interface ShapeModelDataset<IMAGE extends Image<?,IMAGE>>

  • Type Parameters:
    IMAGE - type of the images in the collection
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<IndependentPair<PointList,IMAGE>>, Dataset<IndependentPair<PointList,IMAGE>>, Iterable<IndependentPair<PointList,IMAGE>>, List<IndependentPair<PointList,IMAGE>>, ListDataset<IndependentPair<PointList,IMAGE>>

    public interface ShapeModelDataset<IMAGE extends Image<?,IMAGE>>
extends ListDataset<IndependentPair<PointList,IMAGE>>
    Dataset representing pairs of images and fixed size sets of points, together with a set of connections between points which are valid across all instances. Useful for training PointDistributionModels and ActiveShapeModels.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
